              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 md:order-1 md:mt-0">
            <p class="text-center text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">&copy; <%= currentYear %> Alex Covone. All rights reserved.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
